data.description: Big price reduction. Motivated seller with move in ready home, available for quick close.  Don't miss out on this wonderful well-maintained updated POOL home located west of 41 near Duck Key.  The roof, impact windows, pool, and electric service were all installed in 2018/19 while the AC and hot water heater are about 2 years old. The Kitchen is updated with granite and has a beautiful tile backsplash.  The driveway is wide and long so plenty of room for extra vehicles. The yard is completely fenced with a gate so you can store your RV, boat, trailer, or other toys in privacy. There are NO HOA/Deed restrictions here. This beautiful home is less than a half hour to 3 beaches, minutes to Warm Mineral Springs where water is said to maintain 85 degrees year round and 51 minerals, Cool Today Park, Downtown Wellen, and just 10 min to the new Aquatic Center. Bring your boat, your jet skis, kayaks, and other watercraft. The boat launch area is just 3 minutes away. Enjoy the pool with a working fountain and the backyard with an area for gardening. There is also a shed to store all the yard and pool equipment. The home has a separate indoor laundry room with shelves and cabinets for additional storage. There are 2 closets in the hallway for additional storage space. This home is not in a flood zone so insurance is reasonable.  There are waterways for boating nearby and a public boat ramp. Own a piece of paradise today. This home has an effective year build date of 2010.
